Name: Blue jacket
Short description: A water-repellent jacket that withstands a lot of wind and weather.
Description: This jacket is specially designed for Norwegian conditions. Its water-repellent material will keep any hiker warm and dry on rainy days. The fabric is made of breathable polyester with a soft interior lining of the finest wool, which will keep moisture away.

Name: Green jacket
Short description: A warm wool jacket for colder days
Description: This is a jacket that will keep any hiker warm on cooler days. Its outer fabric is made of pure wool, with a 70% windproof inner lining. The perfect jacket for spring and autumn weather.

Name: Grey jacket
Description: This jacket is perfect for a long hike in the mountains and by the sea on slightly milder days. Its fabric is 100% windproof, but the inside is made of breathable material that allows you to feel warm and fresh all day.

Name: Light grey jacket
Description: Looking to make a statement? Choose Purple Passion to brighten your day.

Name: Orange jacket
Short description: A jacket for working in all conditions.
Description: This work jacket is perfect for harsh weather conditions. Its thick material withstands both the weather and challenging working conditions. Ideal for those who want to stay warm and dry while working outdoors.

Name: Red jacket
Description: This jacket is perfect for a great outdoor workout. Its breathable material makes every exercise a breeze. With outer fabric that is both lightly water-repellent and airy, anyone who enjoys outdoor training will love this jacket.

Name: To grey jacket
Description: This is a jacket suitable for wet and cold conditions. Its special material can withstand temperatures as low as minus 20 degrees Celsius and provides water and wind protection.
